headline.print_headline: Spain's Health Minister Resigns in Kickback Scandal
headline.main: Spain's Health Minister Resigns in Kickback Scandal

lead_paragraph: Spain's Health Minister Ana Mato, whose former husband is linked to a wide-ranging corruption scandal involving Spain's ruling People's Party, said on Wednesday she had presented her resignation from the post.
